    "description": "&quot;Gym Camp Simulator: Prologue&quot; is a limited version of the full game prepared to start running a gym camp on your tropical island right away. Don't forget to add the full version of the game to your wishlist, as many features are restricted in this version.<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084290/extras/2dcc559da6af70b3af9bcc613942d4f2.avif?t=1742839305\" width=616 height=186 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to soak up the sun and experience the ultimate camp adventure in a tropical paradise? Jump into the Gym Camp Simulator and transform your island into a fitness haven! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084290/extras/94d920cc5801deed2cc5782121eab31d.poster.avif?t=1742839305\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084290/extras/94d920cc5801deed2cc5782121eab31d.webm?t=1742839305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084290/extras/94d920cc5801deed2cc5782121eab31d.mp4?t=1742839305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build facilities such as a dorm and gym, craft camp items, and optimize resources to keep the camp running smoothly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084290/extras/c022159e835018fa06c3b5846740369e.poster.avif?t=1742839305\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084290/extras/c022159e835018fa06c3b5846740369e.webm?t=1742839305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084290/extras/c022159e835018fa06c3b5846740369e.mp4?t=1742839305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monitor campers' progress and adjust schedules as needed to keep them on track and happy. Create custom workout routines and prepare meals to help your guests achieve their fitness goals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the tutorial and manage your camp with restricted features to try the game before purchasing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to add the full version of &quot;Gym Camp Simulator&quot; to your wishlist!</p>",
